entry.title: Wisconsin Abortion Clinics Prepare to Resume Appointments
entry.content: Planned Parenthood of Wisconsin is set to offer abortion services again in Milwaukee and Madison, while litigation continues over a previously dormant 1849 state law banning most abortions.
